title: The Romantics to Rodin (Sculpture Art Ebook).pdf
description:
The Romantics to Rodin 
French nineteenth-century sculpture from North American collections 

LA County Museum of Art | 1980 | Pdf | Eng | 368pag | ISBN10 0807609536 | 73.5 MB

The Romantics to Rodin aims to reveal the aesthetic and historical importance of French nineteenth-century sculpture.
The exhibition deals with the period from about 1830 to 1900
